                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2603.24440/2603.24440v1/x1.png",
                "caption": "Figure 1:CUA-SuiteOverview.Human GUI trajectories are recorded across desktop platforms, expert-verified, and annotated with keyframes, bounding boxes, and interaction logs. The resultingCUA-SuitecomprisesUI-Vision, a comprehensive benchmark to evaluate grounding and planning capabilities of computer-use agents;GroundCUA, which consists of densely labeled UI screenshots with 3.6 million annotations;VideoCUA, which comprises 55 hours of video of humans performing computer-use tasks with detailed action trajectories.",
